# Input

```scss
$variable:alpha;
$a:beta;
$b:gamma;
$c:delta;

$test-1:#{something}$variable;
$test-2:$a#{b}$c;
$test-3:#{a}$b#{c};

```


# Formatted

```scss
$variable: alpha;
$a: beta;
$b: gamma;
$c: delta;

$test-1: #{something}$variable;
$test-2: $a#{b}$c;
$test-3: #{a}$b#{c};

```
